casebody.data:
No. 10-6947. Donny Joel Harvey, Petitioner v. Rick Thaler, Director, Texas Department of Criminal Justice, Correctional Institutions Division. 562 U.S. 1129, 131 S. Ct. 910,

178 L. Ed. 2d 740,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 202. January 10, 2011.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Fifth Circuit dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
